{"tid":2015714,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"暗示賠償將涉及天文數字！川普重炮批支那 「100個貿易協議都無法彌補」","createTime":"2020-05-14T01:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T17:17:17.000Z","uid":32511,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ea39a6f98e26fe3e39eefb00f193e10a969b470e","tid":2015714,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T01:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/paNQEDE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FpaNQEDE.jpg&h=0c3b1444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新冠疫情重創美中關係！兩國今年簽署第一階段貿易協議是否生變？近期又因兩國關係緊繃而浮上檯面。美國總統川普今天又再推特放話，表示協議上的墨水還沒乾，世界就因來自中國大陸的瘟疫而受創，「100個貿易協議都無法彌補差額，包括逝去的生命」。<br />\n<br />\n美國共和黨聯邦參議員葛蘭姆（Lindsey Graham）12日提交「新冠病毒究責法案」（TheCOVID-19 Accountability Act），該法案授權美國總統川普，如果大陸拒絕配合國際社會針對新冠病毒起源的調查行動，川普將有權進行一系列制裁行動。<br />\n <br />\n川普今天接受媒體提問時表示，還沒看過法案內容，尊重議員提案。"},{"pid":"b65666e08ba48c9f5a4289532caea9aa8b140507","tid":2015714,"uid":161125,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T01:14:00.000Z","msg":"你地打啦, 好悶呀"},{"pid":"d3d470749c48b7aac5da37354dbb202cb3dcc3f4","tid":2015714,"uid":31637,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T01:14:48.000Z","msg":"霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8cec3a4dd675cbbc6c415740820558c8e95947","tid":2015714,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T01:17:40.000Z","msg":"口交大戰"},{"pid":"d0d8cdc419649e62e9f04b8ff5e1a6884cc8db13","tid":2015714,"uid":237425,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T01:17:55.000Z","msg":"比武漢肺炎害死左美帝8萬幾條人命<br />\n呢條數緊係要計"},{"pid":"439cd781d97ad96bb6b06d8042c73139bc2358eb","tid":2015714,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T01:24:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n放毒呢招係幾高<br />\n試民智不再話下<br />\n重可以封鎖人才同資金流出<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDLLM<br />\n咁